To which she answered, &quot;Be ignorant of your past, but I know you hide from your past and your past does not wish to see your image.&quot; <br>
Now i'm really wondering what's going on, and I sent this tell, &quot;Lady, You are bereft of your sences. What is this past I supposedly hide from?&quot; <br>
