I asked her,&quot; Lady, What hath i done? True I am often in the bazaar for i seek desperatly for research pages I need.&quot;  <br>
She answered, &quot;speak no more to me. you shall never be forgiven though you may have paid with your life, perhaps that is not enough for my pain. &quot;<br>
<br>
Ok so i /report her, and take a couple SS so i have  record of this bizaar conversation. i send an OOC tell in parenthesis stating she has been reported and to leave me alone, there is no IC reason for her attack and tell her goodday. <br>
Phaedrax tells you, '((then you are also Out of line for this was totally IC..and following your own...story ..so if you do not wish to Roleplay it..dont start it))'<br>
